name: MDBX_CHECK
value:
do {                                                                         \
    const int rc = (x);                                                        \
    if (rc != MDBX_SUCCESS) {                                                  \
      printf("Error [%d] %s in %s at %s:%d\n", rc, mdbx_strerror(rc), #x,      \
             __FILE__, __LINE__);                                              \
      exit(EXIT_FAILURE);                                                      \
    }                                                                          \
  } while (0)
